# Asset Attribution

When adding or changing game assets (sprites, audio, fonts, tilesets, etc.):

**Always document asset sources in `README.md`.**

- Add or update an **Acknowledgements** section listing all third-party asset packs
- For each asset: name, creator/source, license, and link if available
- Keep the list current when adding or removing assets
